Discourse Representation&rdquo;, <em>Linguistics and Philosophy</em>,
19(2): 143&ndash;186. doi:10.1007/BF00635836</li>

<li>Neale, Stephen., 1990, <em>Descriptions</em>, Cambridge, MA: MIT
